Node.Notes: Both singular god or plural gods possible here, though plural form of who will go points to gods as more likely (but singular god still possible).
Same issue with singular god or plural gods as in ex32:1. Fact that only one golden bull is made could point to singular god. May also be difference in intent between the people and Aaron.
Plural servants really in apposition to Abraham, Isaac, and Israel.
